ervice performance anomalies**\n   - 各服务如 `cartservice`, `productcatalogservice`, `emailservice` 等的 `rrt_max` 指标在故障期内显示出显著上升。\n   - **原因**: 高延迟通常与下层资源（Node/Pod）的压力有关，进一步体现出 Node 资源问题可能影响到上层服务性能。\n\n### Detected Metrics\n- `node_memory_usage_rate`\n- `pod_cpu_usage`\n- `rrt_max`\n\n### 分析结果 (JSON 格式)\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate exhaustion causing pod degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Memory usage decreased from 34.89% to 29.67%, but p99 rose from 56.21 to 84.37\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage fluctuation detected\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod CPU usage remained static at 0% median, but p99 fluctuated from 0.09 to 0.06\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased due to backend node pressure\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max change ratio observed as 1.441 in cartservice\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些发现表明在故障期间，机器节点资源利用率的显著变化对特定服务性能产生了负面影响。无法将这些问题完全归于某个单一组件，因为资源瓶颈可能涉及多个服务之间的相互影响。将继续进行深入探讨，若有需要请提及进一步详细的分析要求。"}
